  "texts": [
    "In this paper, a systematic methodology has been utilized to conduct a related search on DFIGbased WECS [59].",
    "Additionally, a science mapping approach has been implemented to conduct bibliometric and scientometric analyses using the Scopus online database.",
    "Figure 2 illustrates the methodological process for this study [60].",
    "ScientometricScientometric is a field of study that measures and analyses the production and distribution of scientific literature to examine the publications as indicated in Fig.3 [61].",
    "However, this field is facing challenges due to a lack of consensus on fundamental questions and disapprovals about the quality of its studies from other fields."
  ]
}